# ================================================================================
# PROJECT FUNCTIONS REFERENCE
# ================================================================================
# This file lists the main functions available in this project's R/ directory.
# These functions are loaded automatically when sourcing scripts/01_setup.R

# API Functions (R/api_functions.R):
# - query_pharos_api()         : Query the Pharos API for gene information
# - get_variant_annotations()  : Get variant annotations from multiple sources  
# - batch_query_pharos()       : Batch processing for Pharos API queries

# Data Functions (R/data_functions.R):
# - extract_residue_functions()     : Extract residue function information
# - extract_foldx_predictions()     : Extract FoldX prediction data
# - extract_disease_associations()  : Extract disease association data
# - extract_alphamissense_scores()  : Extract AlphaMissense scores
# - filter_by_rsids()              : Filter data by RS IDs
# - create_summary_table()         : Create summary statistics table

# Plot Functions (R/plot_functions.R):
# - create_foldx_plot()        : Create FoldX prediction plots
# - create_alphamissense_plot(): Create AlphaMissense plots  
# - create_family_plot()       : Create protein family plots
# - save_plot()                : Save plots with standard formatting
# - create_combined_plot()     : Create multi-panel combined plots

# Note: All functions use the tidyverse pipe operator (%>%) which is loaded
# automatically through the tidyverse package.